{"tid":796643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(台灣製造)「MIT商標」也打壓　中國令全面下架","createTime":"2018-08-28T02:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T07:18:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"777f616dc7c7fa5136b4e6d833a76484d68a2938","tid":796643,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180827/640_15ba71c3fec3dadbf39c33480aba93d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180827%2F640_15ba71c3fec3dadbf39c33480aba93d9.jpg&h=22f4454b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國不斷打壓台灣國際空間，現在竟然連MIT（台灣製）商標也不放過！國內的一家生技業董事長透露，銷售到中國的產品竟無預警遭下架，原因是產地僅註明「台灣」，除非改標為「中國台灣區」才能恢復上架。<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》報導，這位董事長表示，一、兩周前中國當地通路商接到官方行文，要求產地僅註明「台灣」、、Made in Taiwan的產品在當天全部下架，完全沒有緩衝時間，包括食品、美妝及生技業者都受到衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n經貿單位證實，從2001年起，中國明文規定產地標示「台灣」的產品可銷往中國，但今年下半年起，卻陸續接到國內業者陳情，標示MIT（台灣製）的產品遭中國海關要求得標示成「中國台灣」或「中國台灣區（意指特別行政區）」等才能通關，否則將被擋關或直接退運。<br />\n<br />\n台商表示為了自救，只好標示「中國台灣」，或以一明一暗雙標籤出口、到當地改標等。對此，知情官員指出，實際上被退關或銷毀數目不多，中國是用政治手段想要在其國內消滅「MIT」，逼迫台商到中國設廠，不然就得在標示上，遵守一中原則。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180827/1418867/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180827%2F1418867%2F&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a9c91183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180827%2F1418867%2F&h=4dee7369\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180827/1418867/</a>"},{"pid":"78232a31e5ea560bcde529db26c8d2e900bdd892","tid":796643,"uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:28:13.000Z","msg":"連唯一安全貨源都自己cut埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係唔係on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵佢地食發瘟豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fcff632caa07b45ebee0ce4ef941c4226e902b","tid":796643,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:30:54.000Z","msg":"呢個標示係日本城堆台灣拖鞋度見過~<br />\n不過入得大陸賣，比人剪牌都好正常<br />\n<br />\n我留名等睇台塑企業改名咪中国台灣企業"},{"pid":"0e54cfbfd6b962b93ec3ee3ef11f00919db7d13a","tid":796643,"uid":130695,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"所以不嬲都話班大陸閪自卑到一個點<br />\n<br />\n靠做埋啲小朋友野打飛機"},{"pid":"feebf858906c604e8d61dcb1ad34c447df151965","tid":796643,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:36:33.000Z","msg":"做埋晒啲濕鳩嘢都改變唔到事實架啦，自己打飛機啦！"},{"pid":"16122728aabc73dcf494f4f85f54b98aa8c6b2e0","tid":796643,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"咁就米撚再賺人民幣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81788213c195986b146efc137faf4eaf5a1c88cf","tid":796643,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國不斷打壓台灣國際空間，現在竟然連MIT（台灣製）商標也不放過！國內的一家生技業董事長透露，銷售到中國的產品竟無預警遭下架，原因是產地僅註明「台灣」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪唔好賣去支那, 開拓海外市場囉<br />\n<br />\njoin us in trade war"},{"pid":"9ddb8a6f36b585693b5a7fa3ee1d50434252a6fb","tid":796643,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16122728aabc73dcf494f4f85f54b98aa8c6b2e0","tid":796643,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"咁就米撚再賺人民幣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"台狗真係好撚無骨氣<br />\n<br />\n明明個世界咁撚大, 目光只見對岸"},{"pid":"12d67a1a2c6572936a8c97360e1fa6744cbe63a9","tid":796643,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddb8a6f36b585693b5a7fa3ee1